            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The provision of a lead consultant and a team of multi-disciplinary Professional Services to undertake the preparation and brief, concept design, developed design, and technical design in accordance with RIBA stages 1-4, and an ongoing design input during the construction period, for the second phase of Public Realm Investment under City Deal in Glasgow City Centre.</P>
