               <CRITERIA_CANDIDATE>
                  <P>It is anticipated that the 6 highest scoring bidders will be invited to tender, where 6 bidders can be identified as having met the minimum criteria for consideration. Where there is a score differential of less than 2% between the 6th placed bidder and subsequent ranking bidders.</P>
                  <P>Those lower ranking bidders will also be shortlisted and invited to tender, up to a maximum of 8 bidders in total. Only if there is a tie at 8 bidders will more than 8 bidders be invited to tender as all the tied bidders will be invited to tender.”.</P>
